      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHRISTMAS STAR (5) meets a few of these much better at the weights and due for a change of luck. Closed strongly with the 59kg with a tough fourth over this trip at Wagga. Value player expected to go close. IOWNA BENZ (1) at her peak for this after she loomed strongly for a narrow second over 1000m at Wagga. Gets map favours and shapes as the main danger. ALL ADORE (2) kept fresh for this after jumping sharply in grade with a fading fifth over 1100m at Wyong in Highway grade. Had excuses from the wide draw on that occasion and assess on the good BM58 win here two-back. Stays in the mix. BOOM IN THE DARK (4) drops sharply in weight and trip after closing late to secure seventh over 1200m at Nowra. Will relish the good tempo and launch late.",
